&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;clause-7wind-farm-operation-maintenance-and-inspections&#34;&gt;Clause 7：Wind farm operation, maintenance and inspections
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;主要构件定义 （参考原报告3.1.20）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB3iec61400-28%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%AF%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB/image-20250416210732791.png&#34;
	width=&#34;786&#34;
	height=&#34;1156&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB3iec61400-28%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%AF%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB/image-20250416210732791_hu_5a6766e5311f925b.png 480w, https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB3iec61400-28%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%AF%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB/image-20250416210732791_hu_6c2f1cf965fb0fbc.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;image-20250416210732791&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;67&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;163px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Principles of risk based inspection (RBI) (see &lt;strong&gt;API 581:2000&lt;/strong&gt;) or reliability -centred maintenance (RCM) (see &lt;strong&gt;IEC 60300-3-11:2009&lt;/strong&gt;) may be applied.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CMS（状态监测系统）可以用于触发或者替换常规的inspection；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Early life inspections (15 % to 25 % through operational life)&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;检测保修期结束前要求的损伤并执行修复；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;作为风机整体状态的基准；&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;建议的检查计划包括：（全部项目请参考&lt;strong&gt;Annex C&lt;/strong&gt;）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://whhong-research.github.io/p/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB3iec61400-28%E9%A3%8E%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%AF%BF%E5%91%BD%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E8%A7%A3%E8%AF%BB/image-20250416212250501.png&#34;
